                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When merchants from different regions encounter each other, the sparks of creativity will invariably fly. For example, someone once said: \"If one could tame a Fungus that had legs, could it help deliver goods and protect our caravans?\" This idea was firmly burned into Azalai's mind, its presence unfading...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Opposing Lineup",
                      "type": "text"
